  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      The purpose of this study is to study the HIV disease progression in HIV-infected Thai Adult.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
  <detailed_description>
    <textblock>
      This is a multicenter, observational prospective cohort study. All HIV-infected patients from
      Bamrasnaradura Institute, Sanpatong Hospital and HIV-NAT, Thai Red Cross AIDS Research
      Centre, are followed to assess HIV disease progression.
    </textblock>
  </detailed_description>
